headline: Adjust: Mobile App Use Grew Globally In 2025 With Continued Move To Multi-Platform
summary: SAN FRANCISCO, February 18, 2026--Leading measurement and analytics company Adjust released today its annual Mobile App Trends report for 2026, revealing continued global growth in app adoption and on-the-go engagement with business, commerce, and entertainment. Global app installs increased 10% year-over-year (YoY) in 2025, while sessions rose 7%, illustrating sustained momentum in mobile app usage. headline: February 2026 Insider Favorites For Growth Stocks
summary: As February 2026 begins, U.S. stock markets are experiencing a robust start with major indices like the Dow Jones and S&P 500 posting significant gains, despite recent economic uncertainties such as government shutdowns and trade negotiations. In this invigorated market environment, investors often look for growth companies with high insider ownership as these stocks can indicate confidence from those closest to the company's operations and strategy.
